// =============================================================================
// Built-in NOCASE vs SQLITE_ENABLE_ICU full-Unicode case folding.
// Spec §15.4.2 — NOCASE limitations.
//
// The default NOCASE collation folds ONLY the ASCII A-Z range. Code paths
// that need Unicode folding must register an ICU-based collation (SQLite
// provides that when built with SQLITE_ENABLE_ICU).
// =============================================================================

module core.database.sqlite.native.nocase_icu_compat_api;

public module policy;
